<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201024/82958f6cba4f40fa8010961fe18bed6e.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">柯桐枝《月光光》68x68cm 2006年</span></img></p>
<p>雄健浑厚、墨色淋漓是柯桐枝花鸟的第一观感，浓淡枯润之墨感、老辣刚直之笔意给观者营造了一个充满诗意的艺术空间。透过各墨之韵感、疏密之布局，动静之设置，仿佛可穿越至宇宙星河中，进行纯粹的思悟，得天地之语，入清雅之境。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201024/e82f391c78974818b8e195d0ddaba142.png" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">柯桐枝《窗花》68x68cm 2009年</span></img></p>
<p>如果说画之外象是吸引观者驻足的原由，那么画之境界则是使得观者反复体悟的本因。观柯桐枝之花鸟，浓淡相宜的墨色极具气韵，其间透露着远离喧嚣尘世的清逸之意，引人不断反复品画、读画，每次观赏总能给观者带来不同的感悟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201024/16c1b7ba54ba457cb6594a43d3d6e0e5.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">柯桐枝《荷潇潇》68x68cm 1999年</span></img></p>
<p>一方案台、一支毛笔、一纸生宣，柯桐枝便在此间蕴发出清新而浑厚的笔墨气息，这种气息既来自前人绘画的启示，更来自于画者充盈的内心及深厚的学养……</p>
➜第25届秋季广州艺博会推荐 | 谢常青
http://www.sohu.com/a/426986753_606561	25315
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201024/f3fe8d6fa05940c6a1034248de677009.png" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">谢常青 | Xie ChangQing</span></img></p>
<p>谢常青早在1990年移居到加利福尼亚，居住在加州菲利蒙特。年轻时喜欢画画。到美国后他到加州奥隆利艺术学院进修三年油画艺术，对欧美艺术史进行研究学习，对西洋油画古典与现代的演进进行了综合体系的探索观摩。在西方油画风格的熏陶下，他的作品已经展示在奥隆利艺术学院画廊，并在弗里蒙特Olive Hyde 艺术协会成员Juried Show和Go Figure拉古纳Plein Air画家协会的人像油画展览。他的人物作品还在国家油画和丙烯酸画家协会的2016年春季国际展览上展出，有来自亚美尼亚、加拿大、德国、以色列、马来西亚、俄罗斯、特立尼达和多巴哥与美国的艺术家。目前是加州艺术俱乐部、国家油画和丙烯酸画家协会的会员和美国油画家协会成员。</p>
<p>Changqing Xie immigrated to California as early as 1990 and lived in Fremont, California. Like to paint when he was young. After arriving in the United States, he went to Ohlone College California to study oil painting art for three years, studied the history of European and American art, and carried out a comprehensive system of exploration and observation of the evolution of oil painting classical and modern . Under the influence of Europe and America oil painting style, his Artworks has been displayed in the Ohlone College Art Gallery, and in the portrait oil painting exhibitions of the members of the Olive Hyde Art Association in Fremont Juried Show and the Go Figure Laguna Plein Air Painters Association. His portrait works were also exhibited at the 2016 Spring International Exhibition of the National Oil and Acrylic Painters Association, featuring artists from Armenia, Canada, Germany, Israel, Malaysia, Russia, Trinidad and Tobago and the United States. He is currently a member of the California Art Club, the National Oil and Acrylic Painters Association, and the American Oil Painters Association.</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
